reviewText: Each story of how God has touched the lives of these Hollywood stars is emotionally compelling.  Denise William's story of faith was especially uplifting and inspirational.  She could be a minister.  Delia Reese is a minister and it shows.  When she tells the story about the miracle of life that she received from God, chills go through me.  It's good to see that there are famous people who really know God.
